title: Bobby Investigates Potential "Catfish" Text + Luke Comb’s Gives Us His Popeye’s Spicy Chicken Sandwich Review + Bobby Gets Meaning From Lindsay Ell About Her New Song “I Don’t Love You”
itunes:title: Bobby Investigates Potential "Catfish" Text + Luke Comb’s Gives Us His Popeye’s Spicy Chicken Sandwich Review + Bobby Gets Meaning From Lindsay Ell About Her New Song “I Don’t Love You”
description:
Bobby got a text message from a girl and investigated it on the air. Luke Combs stops by to talk about the CMA’s, his new album and gives us his Popeye’s Spicy Chicken Sandwich Review. Bobby interviewed his ex-girlfriend Lindsay Ell about her new song “I Don’t Love You”.
